title: Ep. - 436 - HYPE HOUSE BRAVO SHOWS REVIEW
description:
Madeline Roth, Entertainment Editor at Daily Beast, reviews Hype House on Netflix, which follows the lives of each member of the Hype House, a group of content creators who make videos for the social media application TikTok.

 

Jordan Ross Meyers is the creator of @RadziwillLee and @DonnGunvalson accounts on Twitter and the host of the Pretty Corrupt Podcast. Jordan and Kate do a Bravo show rundown.
